Interface FlowInterfaceLimit

All Superinterfaces:

FlowInterfaceLimitImpl
public interface FlowInterfaceLimit
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject

A representation of the model object 'Interface Limit'. Flow interface limit

The following features are supported:

  • Type
  • Status
  • Ref Dir Export Limit
  • Oppsite Ref Dir Import Limit
